berately added; simple resource request coverage does not need Docker or external services.\",\n      \"risks\": [\n        \"Jersey 1.9 and Grizzly 2.1.2 are old; native-image may still require generated reachability metadata for Jersey resource reflection and Grizzly internals.\",\n        \"The JAXB API dependency is enough for ordinary resource endpoint startup and requests, but WADL response generation needs a JAXB implementation such as jaxb-runtime.\"\n      ],\n      \"applied_setup\": [\n        {\n          \"kind\": \"dependency\",\n          \"coordinate\": \"javax.xml.bind:jaxb-api:2.3.1\",\n          \"result\": \"applied\",\n          \"target\": \"tests/src/com.sun.jersey/jersey-grizzly2/1.9/build.gradle\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"input_evidence\": [\n        {\n          \"name\": \"issue\",\n          \"summary\": \"#3158 Support for com.sun.jersey:jersey-grizzly2:1.9; label=library-new-request; body_chars=103\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"existing_tests\",\n          \"summary\": \"0 existing test file path(s) included\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"model\": \"oca/gpt-5.5\",\n      \"input_tokens_used\": 38133,\n      \"output_tokens_used\": 8477,\n      \"prompt_path\": \"library-preflight-prompt.txt\",\n      \"raw_response_path\": \"library-preflight-response.txt\",\n      \"session_log_path\": \"/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/logs/com.sun.jersey:jersey-grizzly2:1.9/library-preparation-preflight/pi-generation-2026-06-28T13-50-15-482363Z.log\"\n    },\n    \"metrics\": {\n      \"input_tokens_used\": 104242,\n      \"cached_input_tokens_used\": 1593344,\n      \"output_tokens_used\": 11398,\n      \"iterations\": 2,\n      \"cost_usd\": 1.1386,\n      \"generated_loc\": 0,\n      \"tested_library_loc\": 0,\n      \"metadata_entries\": 0,\n      \"code_coverage_percent\": 0.0\n    },\n    \"artifacts\": {\n      \"test_file\": \"None\",\n      \"metadata_file\": \"None\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n"